long_description: we started in 1994, a contractor/custom home builder, a banker and a manufacturing engineer. we then proceeded to bring the distribution of solatube skylights to the state of washington. we sell the solatube installed and as diy kits to homeowners and also distribute to contractors, roofers and other businesses. now the solar star solar powered attic fan is the brand of choice. we are committed to quality installations of our products by our qualified employees. our hope is for our installations today to be our references and referrals tomorrow. that's our story; we invite you to call us today for a free consultation 425-744-1211. solatube daylighting systems combine breakthrough optical technology with advanced designs and the highest quality materials to fill your living spaces with an abundance of pure, clear natural light. from sunup to sundown, daylight is harvested by a specially designed rooftop dome that uses proprietary raybender 3000 technology. solatube...the brightest idea since the creation of the sun.

generated_description: nw natural lighting is a company that specializes in providing natural lighting solutions for homes and businesses. they offer solatube daylighting systems that combine optical technology with advanced designs and high-quality materials to provide pure, clear natural light for living spaces. their products are designed to transform dark spaces, such as hallways, entryways, stairwells, and closets, into bright and inviting areas that are often overlooked when it comes to lighting. nw natural lighting joined beehaven inc. in may of 2018 and is committed to being a growing and innovative company. they sell solatubes as installed and diy kits to homeowners, contractors, roofers, and other businesses, and distribute to other businesses as well. the company also offers custom railing, solar attic fans, and retractable screens. nwnaturallighting is dedicated to providing quality products and excellent customer service.
